8 In any city other than a city not within a county, real property subject to partial tax abatement
9 under either the provisions of the urban redevelopment corporations law of Missouri or the
10 provisions of sections 99.700 to 99.710 shall for the purpose of assessment and collection of
11 ad valorem real estate taxes levied under the provisions of this section be assessed and ad
12 valorem real estate taxes shall be collected as if the real estate were not subject to the tax
