21 cents by application of section 137.073 or 137.115, whichever is applicable, it shall not be
22 necessary to further reduce such county's tax rate due to the attainment of such first class
23 county status.
137.073. 1. As used in this section, the following terms mean:
2 (1) "General reassessment", changes in value, entered in the assessor's books, of a
