99 property in the aggregate by different amounts, the tax rate that shall be used for the single tax
100 rate calculation shall be a blended rate, calculated in the manner provided under subdivision
101 (1) of subsection 6 of this section.]
102 (5) Notwithstanding any provision of this subsection to the contrary, no revision to
103 the rate of levy for personal property shall cause such levy to increase over the levy for
