23 purpose] as provided in subsection 1 of section 115.706. Such resolution shall set forth the
24 project name for the proposed sewage or storm water facility improvement, the general nature
25 of the proposed improvement, the estimated cost of such improvement, the boundaries of the
26 proposed sewage or storm water facility improvement district to be assessed, and the
27 proposed method or methods of assessment, including any provision for the annual
28 assessment of maintenance costs of the improvement in each year after the bonds issued for
